data.title: Tokheim India is the first company who got " Best Fast Diagram" Award internationally ….
data.meta_description: Tokheim India presented “Value Engineering Study of Fuel Dispenser” project in International Value Engineering conference which was held at Bangalore, TIPL has been awarded for “Best FAST Diagram Trophy”.
